_sText:
I made this map in about an hour or 2.
its nothing special just a small little gun game map.
there is no nav file with it you should be able to 
make one in about 30 seconds. 
i would recommend smaller servers use this map as it is very small.
i was going to do a 3d skybox, and I actually had one made but i do believe it was way too small. after i compiled it the map just wouldn't even load, so i left the other shapes out. I might do an expanded version a bigger with more stuff in it.
